## ğŸ§® Example Input

```js
const messages = [
  {
    role: "user",
    content: "Add 3 and 4. multiply by 2 and sub by 1 ",
  },
];
```

Expected Output:

```js
{
  messages: [
    {
      role: "assistant",
      content: "The result is 13.",
    },
  ];
}
```

